strings:
<voice_0x0100139C><se_high>Red: Wot took ya so long!?
Looks like the goodies are mine, eh!?
We did say it was first come first served!

<voice_0x0100139D><se_low>Captain Crow: Ahoy there, they call me Cap'n Crow.
Long ago, I were one o' the pirates who sailed the seven seas...

<voice_0x0100139E><se_low>Captain Crow: Think you can take my treasure, do ya?
Think you've got what it takes?
<voice_0x0100139F><se_low>Captain Crow: Yo, ho, ho, then prove it by fightin' me.
<voice_0x010013A0><se_low>Captain Crow: Else get your hands off me jewels!

<voice_0x010013A1><se_high>Red: Oh...
Fightin' ain't really my cuppa tea, but...
<voice_0x010013A2><se_low>Yangus: Red! Wot you doin' gettin' yerself into this!?
